Folder Changed Trigger for Hudson CI
(c) 2010 Burc Sade, http://burcsade.com/

Folder Changed Trigger for Hudson CI is released under the MIT license.

Folder Changed Trigger for Hudson CI is a trigger plugin for Hudson CI 
to check for folder and/or subfolder changes and trigger builds. It is
meant to be an example for anyone who wants to go deeper into building
plugins for Hudson CI. If you find it useful and/or have questions 
you can drop me an email.

burcsade(at)gmail(dot)com


Related links:

Hudson CI web site
http://hudson-ci.org/

